%%{init: {'theme': 'dark'}}%%
flowchart LR
    Upload[Document Upload<br/>S3 / Local] --> Validate[Validate + Malware Scan]
    Validate --> Extract[Text Extraction<br/>pypdf / unstructured]
    Extract --> Normalize[Normalize + Boilerplate Removal]
    Normalize --> Detect[Document Type Detection]
    Detect --> Chunk[High-Quality Clinical Chunking]
    Chunk --> Metadata[Attach Rich Metadata<br/>tenant, patient, consent, sensitivity]
    Metadata --> Embed[Generate Titan / Local Embeddings]
    Embed --> StoreVector[(Amazon OpenSearch<br/>or pgvector)]
    StoreVector --> StoreMeta[(RDS PostgreSQL)]
    StoreMeta --> Audit[Write Audit Event]
    Audit --> Metrics[Emit Ingestion Metrics]
